    <note>Liu(2) Shu [1230] Uncle of Ningzhi's [1217] father, Gong [3597]. Liu(2) Anzhi [3579] (CBD, based on Zhao(1) Dingchen, has mingzi as Anzheng, thereby creating great confusion) was Wang(2) Anli's [1760] son-in-law. Anzhi's wife was the sister of Zhao(1) Dingchen's [395] wife. Shu's son-in-law, Chen(1) Shu [3082], was the father-in-law of Pan(1) Jinggui's [1386] father, Haogu [3692]. Liu Yizhi, WJ, 51.12b-15b (wife, born Fu(5), who died in 1118 at age 78 [has information on jiafa; she was well-educated at age 18--this was second marriage after marrying a Shi(4)]; Zhao Dingchen, WJ, 18.5a; XCB, 209.11b; SHY:ZG, 65.23a; SS, 321.14b-15a; Wang Zao, WJ, 25.15a; Wuxing zhi, 17.4a. CBD, 5, 3858-9.</note>
